@startuml seq-post-creation
participant Browser
participant "Posts Service" as PS
participant "Users Service" as US
participant "Posts DB" as DB

Browser -> PS: POST /posts {content} [Bearer JWT]
PS -> US: GET /users/{author_id}
US --> PS: 200 OK {profile}
PS -> DB: INSERT post
PS --> Browser: 201 Created {post}
@enduml
